animeTitle: Dragon Ball Z Movie 9 – Bojack Unbound
otherNames: Dragon Ball Z Movie 09: Ginga Girigiri!! Bucchigiri No Sugoi Yatsu, Dragon Ball Z: Super Guy In The Galaxy, Dragon Ball Z: The Galaxy Is In Danger!! The Super Awesome Guy, ドラゴンボールZ 銀河ギリギリ!! ぶっちぎりの凄い奴
synopsis: Mr. Money is holding another Tenka'ichi Budokai and Mr. Satan invites everyone in the world to join in. Little does he know that Bojack, an ancient villain who has escaped his prison, is competing. Since Goku is currently dead, it is up to Gohan, Vegita, and Trunks to defeat Bojack and his henchman.
